features: [Premium PVC Material & Anti-Faded Ink for Long-Term Use] The vintage garage signs are constructed from durable and flexible PVC to help them last longer. You'll never have to worry about them being bent when delivering or in future use. In addition to their waterproof and rustproof PVC material, the vintage car wall decors are printed with UV-treated ink, which enables them to maintain good fade resistance in strong sunlight or heavy rain.

[Duplex Printing with Rustic & Weathered Effects] Out of all the vintage signs for garage you can find, these old car decors are the awesome ones as each piece is double-sided printed with high-quality images along with a matt finish. They are managed to achieve a retro-weathered appearance both tactilely and visually, with simulated scratches and frayed edges on each side. Try your hand at these signs if you are seeking a more retro sign to highlight your vintage wall decor.

[5 PCS Vintage Car Signs Set] Consisted of 5 pieces with each measuring 8*12 inches, the signs for garage decor follow along the usual vintage theme seen in many wall art decorations for man caves. They are built on classic oil or car brands advertisement, featuring vintage weathered looks. Hanging these retro signs together or scattered around your space is an easy way to spruce up your personal realm and bring you back to the "good old days."

[Pre-Punched Hole for Easy Decor] There are 4 small holes pre-drilled into each corner of the vintage car decor so that you can simply mount them with a fine rope or screws. You can also liven up your garage space with ease by sticking them to the wall using double-sided tape, as they're lightweight and won't come off easily. Furthermore, the corners of these retro wall decors are rounded to prevent you from getting hurt during installation.

[Retro Room Decor & Unique Gift] Garage decors for men cave decor have a vintage feel from the classic advertisement image down to the faded weathered detail on the surface. Therefore, they perform well to create a special touch to the man cave, bedroom, backyard, patio, garage, office, cafe, bar, etc. This garage posters set would also be an awesome gift. If you know someone who is interested in retro decor, then this old-fashioned sign is right up his alley.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: We can't go back to the good old days, but we can decorate our house to create a retro vibe! Made from a combination of classic gas stations, American automotive history, and vintage signage, Eastlink garage signs are designed to create an ideal home decor sign that brings you a vintage and retro touch. All the signs, crafted with PVC material, are full of the flavors of the old days with printed scratches and fading on both surfaces. They look as if they've withstood some harsh winds or dust over the years, which are suitable for use as decorations or as gifts for friends.

Product Detail Duplex HD Printing The vintage signs for man cave are duplex printed with high-quality imagery with imitative scratches and rust on them. Compared to other single-sided printed signs, these signs have a more authentic retro feel. Pre-Drilled Mounting Holes Featured with 4 pre-drilled small holes in the 4 corners, the signs can easily be fixed onto walls with nails or rope. Super easy to decorate indoors or outdoors. Bend Resistant PVC Material Be sure to keep an eye on the flexible and durable PVC material that we have adopted. It is because of this that our vintage car wall decor will arrive at your location safely, free of dents and creases.

Anti Scratch The PVC material used for the signs is flexible, resistant, and sturdy. Accompanied with a matt finish, they are more likely to withstand accidental scratches and harsh winds in long time use than other signs. Anti Fade The UV-treated ink printed on the signs enables the beautiful color to withstand the test of time and weather. Therefore, signs are fade-resistant -- even when installed in heavy rain and strong sunlight. Anti Rust Thanks to the unique PVC material our garage decor signs are made of, they are waterproof and rust-proof. There is no need to worry about the sign being corroded even if it is decorated outdoors on a rainy day.

Specification Size: Each sign is 12 inches long by 8 inches tall. Style: Vintage retro style with weathered and aged finishes. Material: Flexible and durable Polyvinyl Chloride Package Included: 5x vintage garage signs (Designed from combinations of elements from classic oil and gas brands, American automotive history, and vintage advertising signage.) Warmly Note: Stay away from high-temperature environments.
Bring retro flair and keep the monotony out of your life!

reviews.reviewTitle: Better than I thought they would be
reviews.reviewText: Signs that look rustic but won't rust away, so glad I went with these. The print quality is fantastic too, my wife thought they were real metal signs when I had them laid out on the table.The best thing is these are lighter than steel and waterproof so I can put them anywhere. They are printed both sides too so if one side ever fades just turn it over. Makes it especially useful for placing in a window.Highly recommended.
